---
---

<section class="prac-note" aria-label="A note from Ilshat">
  <div class="prac-inner reveal">
    <figure class="prac-portrait-figure">
      <div class="prac-portrait-frame">
        <img
          src="/assets/founder-portrait.jpg"
          alt="Ilshat, practitioner"
          class="prac-portrait"
          width="560"
          height="720"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';"
        />
        <div class="prac-portrait-fallback" aria-hidden="true" style="display:none;">
          <span>I.S.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <figcaption class="prac-portrait-cap">
        Ilshat —
        <a href="https://youtube.com/@Ilshatai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@Ilshatai</a>
      </figcaption>
    </figure>

    <div class="prac-text">
      <p class="prac-body">
        I take four engagements a month because I do the analysis myself. The price equals
        five days of focused work — sent in writing on the discovery call. There is no
        money-back guarantee. Instead, you get a sample audit before you pay, and a
        twenty-minute call so you can decide whether I am the right person. If I am not,
        I will tell you on the call.
      </p>
      <p class="prac-sig">— Ilshat</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .prac-note {
    background: var(--color-cream);
    color: var(--color-ink);
    padding: clamp(72px, 10vw, 120px) 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-mist);
  }

  .prac-inner {
    max-width: 1040px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .prac-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 38fr 62fr;
    }
  }

  .prac-portrait-figure {
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.875rem;
  }

  .prac-portrait-frame {
    position: relative;
    width: min(280px, 100%);
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 18px;
    outline: 1px solid rgba(217, 119, 87, 0.5);
    outline-offset: 6px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(20, 20, 19, 0.08);
    transition: transform 500ms cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1);
    will-change: transform;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .prac-portrait-frame:hover {
      transform: rotate(-1.5deg) translateY(-4px);
    }
  }

  .prac-portrait {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
  }

  .prac-portrait-fallback {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--color-cream-soft);
    color: var(--color-amber);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 96;
    font-size: 52px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .prac-portrait-cap {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--color-stone);
    margin-left: 6px;
  }

  .prac-portrait-cap a {
    color: var(--color-amber);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: rgba(217, 119, 87, 0.35);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: text-decoration-color 200ms ease;
  }

  .prac-portrait-cap a:hover {
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-amber);
  }

  .prac-text {
    max-width: 56ch;
  }

  .prac-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(1.0625rem, 1.6vw, 1.25rem);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .prac-sig {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 72, 'SOFT' 50;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-amber);
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
